data.description: Why wait months for NV Homes to build a basic model when you can enjoy an ALREADY BUILT upgraded 2022 Baldwin model with over 4000 square feet?  Some of the features you’ll love: a covered deck off the massive kitchen, sun-filled open floor plan, fully finished walkout basement with a full bath, bedroom-level laundry room complete with a utility sink, primary bedroom custom closets, and custom lighting.  All of this located within Patuxent Greens, an exclusive and new community with amenities including a tennis court, playground, walking trails, ponds, and a future clubhouse with a pool and fitness center.  LIST PRICE ALREADY APPROVED BY SHORT SALE LENDER.  ALL additional terms subject to 3rd party approval.
